      <h2>Why Build Fast with Bubble?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>No-code lets you go from idea to customer feedback in days, not months.</li>
        <li>Iterate rapidly with a true visual builder—no backend or code deployment headaches!</li>
        <li>Integrated database, authentication, and payments make Bubble perfect for SaaS MVPs.</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>My Workflow in 10 Days</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Days 1-2:</strong> Mapped the MVP must-haves (user login, core dashboard, billing).</li>
        <li><strong>Days 3-4:</strong> Built UI in Bubble’s editor—looks great, works on all devices.</li>
        <li><strong>Day 5:</strong> Structured databases for users, subscriptions, and app data.</li>
        <li><strong>Day 6:</strong> Integrated Stripe for payments—Bubble API Connector rocks.</li>
        <li><strong>Days 7-8:</strong> Added notifications, automated emails, first user onboarding.</li>
        <li><strong>Day 9:</strong> Internal tests and staged feedback, tweaks, improvements.</li>
        <li><strong>Day 10:</strong> Launched and started iterating with real users!</li>
      </ol>
      <h2>Lessons Learned</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Keep your first version simple—get feedback, then improve.</li>
        <li>Bubble’s workflows and conditions allow powerful logic, fast.</li>
        <li>Documentation your best friend when doing custom integrations.</li>
